# Coding Rules for Netabare Project

- Use Vue 3 Composition API for components (no Options API unless specified).
- Use Pinia for state management.
- Use Vue Router for routing.
- Style with TailwindCSS classes in templates (e.g., "p-4 mt-2").
- Use ESM syntax (import/export) for JavaScript.
- Prefer "dayjs" for date/time over "moment".
- Use "axios" for HTTP requests.
- Keep code formatted per Prettier and linted per ESLint (Vue/JS rules)
